Build the Docker Image:
    docker build -t flask-vulnerable-app .

Run the Docker Container:
    docker run -d -p 5000:5000 flask-vulnerable-app

Run the Flask App in Docker:
    docker run -d -p 5000:5000 flask-vulnerable-app

File Structure

flask-vulnerable-app/
├── app.py
├── Dockerfile
├── requirements.txt
├── docker-compose.yml  # (Optional)
├── templates/
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── login.html
│   ├── signup.html
│   └── admin.html
└── uploads/  # (Folder to store uploaded files)
└── vulnerable.db  # (SQLite database file)
